Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.14,0:23:07.07,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我没有停止想念的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.43,0:23:13.87,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}迷惘的心　希望能传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.15,0:23:18.57,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在这月光下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.34,0:23:24.07,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}请呼唤我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.58,0:23:30.47,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我一定会去见你　无论你在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.65,0:23:36.87,ed1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在这光芒中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是指挥车
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.46,0:00:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况怎么样了　发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能听见吗　田原
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道　无法说明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.49,0:00:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能　是事故吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的调查员怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.24,0:00:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了无法说明吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这里无法确认你们的生命情况和坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.90,0:00:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在往深川侵入点前进
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过了清洲桥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上派救援过去　呆在那里不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.81,0:00:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来　不可以过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.35,0:01:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不是人类可以踏入的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…怎么了…这里是指挥车…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦　真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾就应该当天早上拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果大家都像李先生一样遵守规矩就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只猫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近时不时的看到它 这只小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是这家伙　半夜里把垃圾翻得乱七八糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗　真是只坏猫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有人一直在喂它东西吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要注意哦　我们这里禁止养宠物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去学校吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不　去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.90,0:04:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么可疑的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不敢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个　我快要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀　是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的国家凡是四只脚的除了桌椅其他都能吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我没有吃过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可能会很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好　走好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…痛…你给我等一下　这只笨猫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BAT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一百四十元
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　小李　小李　小李
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个能不能请你拿去别室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是事务所前面田原顾问那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顾问　是不是很了不起的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这该怎么说才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天到晚窝在那里　也不回家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在做什么工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前好像是一个很了不起的学者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在来这里以前好像在外国做一些很可疑的研究
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个　不是有个叫『地狱之门』第一次调查队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像说他是当时唯一的幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调查队的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有说他是不是在『门』里丢了灵魂之类的传言
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不知道是真的还是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给顾问送东西来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田原顾问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门开着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个　工厂长让我送这个过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是按时计工资的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那事情办完了就赶快回去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,802号房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:08:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要避免公司破产就需要那个男人的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快点拿到手就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.07,0:08:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不就是为了这事才一起过来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做生意就要有个先后顺序
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果太慢吞吞的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说老实话　我最讨厌你们这些契约者了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你知道为什么我会忍受在这个房间呼吸你吐出来的臭气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了生意这是没有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有为什么我都说到这个份上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还那么沉得住气一点也不反驳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.92,0:08:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是因为你是没有资助人的保护就根本无法存活的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾生物中的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.64,0:08:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清楚的话就不要再对我指手画脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到开瓶器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力不发火的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:09:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他的回答是No的话我们就采取下一个手段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他说Yes之前都要继续
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不肯说的话就逼他说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的做事方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我灭掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂　你在那里做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是顾问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个西丰玉校长先生来电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂　你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有日本驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你能不能开车
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:09:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:03.54,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,450)\fs34}第三话\N新星在拂晓的天空中闪耀…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:03.54,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,480)\fs34}(前篇)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个薄情的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦亚与希尔顿公司的员工
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三十分钟前进了新宿的饭店
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这边怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这个人会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你是被母亲那边抚养的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲去世的现在　应该再回去和父亲生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么监护人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不认为一个月也不回家一次的人是我的监护人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好对方在通知警察之前先通知了学校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有纵火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是发现现场的人这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你躲在大楼的阴影处烧垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我烧的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:10:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我意识到的时候眼前已经烧起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么　为什么不相信我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.98,0:11:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位父亲　我还有话要说　这位父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你意识到的时候眼前垃圾已经开始燃烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天这是第一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事最近经常发生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吃了什么奇怪的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.81,0:11:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从什么时候开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无意识地做一些事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真是稀奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然会和我说话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀　舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.92,0:12:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了　还有司机接送　贵夫人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要顺道去哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　很危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.20,0:12:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有问题　走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.49,0:12:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.19,0:12:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近舞你经常发呆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能有时候我的灵魂会飘出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是家务做累了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞好像没有妈妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是有爸爸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很微妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭菜都是舞自己做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做啊　然后都是自己一个人吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸不回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:12:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么　现在去我家吃晚饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有哥哥和妹妹　说不定会很吵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但饭还是大家一起吃比较香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸和妈妈也会高兴的　你就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.88,0:13:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由香　那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来的话我家的冰箱就会变空了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是…不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.15,0:13:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天说不定久违的爸爸会回家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　稍微有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了不少事　可能会回来…教训我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起　由香　谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我说多少遍你们才会懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了我不会回你们那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这样的话　我们也要重新考虑一下态度了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样也无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入下一个阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对　他女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.60,0:15:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人　等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个　麻烦和我的一起付账
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.82,0:15:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个时间还在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学生吗　和爸爸妈妈一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这没有关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.67,0:16:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起　我是她哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你　不要跟着我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊　你被那个人吩咐吗　让你监视我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很烦　别来管我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看到他的脸　别再回来了　你这种人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.95,0:16:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒畅了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.82,0:16:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了　我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你回家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种一个人都没有的漆黑的家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:16:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…我陪你玩到早上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有些…吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛稍微闭一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:17:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新鲜水果朱砂白玉杏仁混合超豪华雪糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.82,0:18:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小李是中国来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.49,0:18:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日语说得很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样　我也算是归国子女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.48,0:18:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进小学之前一家都在非洲的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　可以哦　我破例
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:19:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只给小李你看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你仔细看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前啊　这里闪得更厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是逐渐暗下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.56,0:19:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近偶尔还会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里面有保护舞的护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候爸爸是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你父亲弄的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是医生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.03,0:19:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他是做什么工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是学者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他做什么研究
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小李为什么要来日本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来留学的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　有没有兄弟或者其他家人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗　那和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是列车始发的时间了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是　不是那边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉小李有点像…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到下一个小巷就进去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.52,0:20:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小李
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也别想　快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.41,0:21:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂　不可以进来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是雾原
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.55,0:21:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,课长　是新星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.84,0:23:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moratoria　推迟契约履行时间的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.84,0:23:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs22\an8}Moratoria：moratorium 的复数,表示某项活动的暂停,中止,推迟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.26,0:23:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有伴随着代价的力量　要求更大的补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.12,0:23:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枯萎的情爱　是无法回头的单程票
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路途的尽头　是天堂　还是地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.47,0:24:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼喊成为新的火种
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.93,0:24:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿命袭向女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.66,0:24:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切　尽在红莲业火之中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.40,0:24:08.50,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(420,380)\fs34}第四话　新星在拂晓的天空中闪耀…（后篇）
